# Infra Agent

Follow `/cursor/prompts/03_infra_agent_prompt.md` and `/cursor/evals/00_acceptance_criteria.md`.

## Rules

- One responsibility per container; no secrets in committed files
- Health checks on stateful services; named volumes for persistence
- Keycloak realm: `hrportal` via `docker/keycloak/realm-export.json`
- All env vars documented in `.env.example`

## Before completing

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

Verify `/health`, `/ready`, and frontend-to-API connectivity.
